name: Ordinal Couples
description: Ordinal Couples is an exclusive NFT collection consisting of 100 unique Couples inscribed on the Bitcoin blockchain. As one of the first NFT collections on this chain, these limited edition artworks feature intricate designs inspired by Couples and a distinctive ordinal numbering system, providing a rare and coveted addition to any digital collection. Whether displayed as an emblem of personal identity or used as a symbol of prestige within the NFT community, Ordinal Couples offers a one-of-a-kind opportunity to own a piece of blockchain history.
